metadata.description:
As the world economy deteriorates, leading to the downfall of low income, famous pepeverse celebrities begin to exchange in their most beloved treasure for cryptocurrency believing that the market will return a fortune.

Inspired by Roman Women Offering Their Jewellery in Defence of the State - Vincenzo Camuccini (1825-1829)
